1) make FastAPI API
(CRUD)
- Create: duh
- Delete: duh
- Read:
  - GET /agents
  - GET /agents/{}/memory
- Update: chat loop
  - POST /session/create
    - sid + initial message if necessary
  - POST /session/send-message
    - send message, get agent response + if outer loop ran (if N messages, optimiser+summariser runs right after inner loop)
  - GET /session/events
    - polls for proactive agent message during session due to inactivity/before session

2) humanlikeness+impulsiveness+enthusiasm-shyness trait determines if agent start convo/agent proactive nudge
  - base probability
    - personality factor = clamp_0_1((impulsiveness/10)+(enthusiasm/40)-(shyness/20))
    - base proactive probability = (humanlikeness/10)*personality factor
  - convo start probability = base proactive probability 
  - nudge during convo = base prob, with exponential backoff (time) increasing after sent proactive msg (base interval ~2min, backoff ~45s), resets when user replies
  - nudge during convo = base prob, with exponential backoff (time) increasing after sent proactive msg (much higher base interval eg 2h + backoff eg 30min)

3) make Textual (https://github.com/Textualize/textual) TUI/webpage n host 
